  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mouselash is a satisfying action roguelite where you are the mouse cursor.  Swipe and slice through waves of enemies as you create your custom build of weapons and stats every run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/6c7d888fd66157d9be371251f8cd549b.poster.avif?t=1729526614\" width=616 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/6c7d888fd66157d9be371251f8cd549b.webm?t=1729526614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/6c7d888fd66157d9be371251f8cd549b.mp4?t=1729526614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick and satisfying runs (<30 mins)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40+ weapons, each having unique tags and stats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ items to synergize with your weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15+ characters, each with unique modifiers and builds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scaling difficulty levels to test your improving skills</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/29f5f5a83e177c9bb8d7d47683fbe867.poster.avif?t=1729526614\" width=556 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/29f5f5a83e177c9bb8d7d47683fbe867.webm?t=1729526614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/29f5f5a83e177c9bb8d7d47683fbe867.mp4?t=1729526614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swipe your cursor to damage enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your weapons help clear the waves in various ways</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After every round, upgrade your build in the shop</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/90939d1913499cfe5966614c402a64b2.poster.avif?t=1729526614\" width=556 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/90939d1913499cfe5966614c402a64b2.webm?t=1729526614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/90939d1913499cfe5966614c402a64b2.mp4?t=1729526614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mouselash is a satisfying action roguelite where you are the mouse cursor.  Swipe and slice through waves of enemies as you create your custom build of weapons and stats every run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/6c7d888fd66157d9be371251f8cd549b.poster.avif?t=1729526614\" width=616 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/6c7d888fd66157d9be371251f8cd549b.webm?t=1729526614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/6c7d888fd66157d9be371251f8cd549b.mp4?t=1729526614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick and satisfying runs (<30 mins)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40+ weapons, each having unique tags and stats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ items to synergize with your weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15+ characters, each with unique modifiers and builds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scaling difficulty levels to test your improving skills</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/29f5f5a83e177c9bb8d7d47683fbe867.poster.avif?t=1729526614\" width=556 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/29f5f5a83e177c9bb8d7d47683fbe867.webm?t=1729526614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/29f5f5a83e177c9bb8d7d47683fbe867.mp4?t=1729526614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swipe your cursor to damage enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your weapons help clear the waves in various ways</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After every round, upgrade your build in the shop</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/90939d1913499cfe5966614c402a64b2.poster.avif?t=1729526614\" width=556 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/90939d1913499cfe5966614c402a64b2.webm?t=1729526614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210870/extras/90939d1913499cfe5966614c402a64b2.mp4?t=1729526614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
